DOC.brief_summary: The investigators aimed to compare the efficacy of nasal SIMV and nasal CPAP in patients with wet lung.
DOC.brief_title: Comparison of Nasal CPAP and Nasal SIMV in Transient Tachypnea of Newborn
DOC.detailed_description: We aimed to compare two types of ventilatory support in cases of transient tachypnea of newborn who are >35 gestational week.
DOC.criteria: >35 gestational week wetlung major congenital anomalies
DOC.keyword: infants who are >35 gestational week with wet lung
